Package: knitrProgressBar
Type: Package
Title: Provides Progress Bars in Knitr
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person(given = c("Robert", "M"), family = "Flight", email = "rflight79@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a progress bar that can write to a variety of locations, 
    including stdout, stderr, or a file. Useful when using `knitr` or `rmarkdown::render`
    and you still want to see progress of calculations in the terminal.
